Spec: Unknown Sections Sampler

Purpose:
  Verify that non-canonical section names are preserved as unknown_sections
  with their original casing and full line content.

Custom Header:
  This section's name isn't in the canonical SpecDD list.
  It should appear in unknown_sections.

Another Unknown:
  Single-line body.

Mixed Bag:
  Body line one.
  Body line two.
  Body line three.
